:"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:180.1":{"pli":"Na dhammo nāyatanaṁ? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:181.1":{"pli":"Nāyatanā na sotaṁ? …pe… ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:182.1":{"pli":"Na dhammo nāyatanaṁ? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:183.1":{"pli":"Nāyatanā na mano? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse' data-counter='12'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:184.1":{"pli":"(Cakkaṁ bandhitabbaṁ.) ","html":"<p class='end'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.1:184.2":{"pli":"Paṇṇattiuddesavāro. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"ya3.1.2":{"ya3.1.2:0.1":{"pli":"3 Āyatanayamaka ","html":"<article id='ya3.1.2'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"ya3.1.2:0.2":{"pli":"3.1 Paṇṇattivāra ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"ya3.1.2:0.3":{"pli":"3.1.2. Paṇṇattivāraniddesa ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"ya3.1.2:1.0.1":{"pli":"3.1.2.1. Padasodhanavāra ","html":"<h2>{}</h2>"},"ya3.1.2:1.0.2":{"pli":"3.1.2.1.1. Anuloma ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya3.1.2:1.1":{"pli":"Cakkhu cakkhāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:2.1":{"pli":"Dibbacakkhu paññācakkhu cakkhu, na cakkhāyatanaṁ. Cakkhāyatanaṁ cakkhu ceva cakkhāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:3.1":{"pli":"Cakkhāyatanaṁ cakkhūti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:4.1":{"pli":"Sotaṁ sotāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:5.1":{"pli":"Dibbasotaṁ taṇhāsotaṁ sotaṁ, na sotāyatanaṁ. Sotāyatanaṁ sotañceva sotāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:6.1":{"pli":"Sotāyatanaṁ sotanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:7.1":{"pli":"Ghānaṁ ghānāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:8.1":{"pli":"Ghānāyatanaṁ ghānanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:9.1":{"pli":"Jivhā jivhāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:10.1":{"pli":"Jivhāyatanaṁ jivhāti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:11.1":{"pli":"Kāyo kāyāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:12.1":{"pli":"Kāyāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso kāyo, na kāyāyatanaṁ. Kāyāyatanaṁ kāyo ceva kāyāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:13.1":{"pli":"Kāyāyatanaṁ kāyoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:14.1":{"pli":"Rūpaṁ rūpāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:15.1":{"pli":"Rūpāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ rūpaṁ, na rūpāyatanaṁ. Rūpāyatanaṁ rūpañceva rūpāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:16.1":{"pli":"Rūpāyatanaṁ rūpanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:17.1":{"pli":"Saddo saddāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:18.1":{"pli":"Saddāyatanaṁ saddoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:19.1":{"pli":"Gandho gandhāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:20.1":{"pli":"Sīlagandho samādhigandho paññāgandho gandho, na gandhāyatanaṁ. Gandhāyatanaṁ gandho ceva gandhāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:21.1":{"pli":"Gandhāyatanaṁ gandhoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:22.1":{"pli":"Raso rasāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:23.1":{"pli":"Attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso raso, na rasāyatanaṁ. Rasāyatanaṁ raso ceva rasāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:24.1":{"pli":"Rasāyatanaṁ rasoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:25.1":{"pli":"Phoṭṭhabbo phoṭṭhabbāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:26.1":{"pli":"Phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṁ phoṭṭhabboti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:27.1":{"pli":"Mano manāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:28.1":{"pli":"Manāyatanaṁ manoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:29.1":{"pli":"Dhammo dhammāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:30.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso dhammo, na dhammāyatanaṁ. Dhammāyatanaṁ dhammo ceva dhammāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:31.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ dhammoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:32.0":{"pli":"3.1.2.1.2. Paccanīka ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya3.1.2:32.1":{"pli":"Na cakkhu na cakkhāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:33.1":{"pli":"Na cakkhāyatanaṁ na cakkhūti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:34.1":{"pli":"Dibbacakkhu paññācakkhu na cakkhāyatanaṁ, cakkhu. Cakkhuñca cakkhāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva cakkhu na ca cakkhāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:35.1":{"pli":"Na sotaṁ na sotāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:36.1":{"pli":"Na sotāyatanaṁ na sotanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:37.1":{"pli":"Dibbasotaṁ taṇhāsotaṁ na sotāyatanaṁ, sotaṁ. Sotañca sotāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva sotaṁ na ca sotāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:38.1":{"pli":"Na ghānaṁ na ghānāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:39.1":{"pli":"Na ghānāyatanaṁ na ghānanti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:40.1":{"pli":"Na jivhā na jivhāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:41.1":{"pli":"Na jivhāyatanaṁ na jivhāti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:42.1":{"pli":"Na kāyo na kāyāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:43.1":{"pli":"Na kāyāyatanaṁ na kāyoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:44.1":{"pli":"Kāyāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso na kāyāyatanaṁ, kāyo. Kāyañca kāyāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva kāyo na ca kāyāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:45.1":{"pli":"Na rūpaṁ na rūpāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:46.1":{"pli":"Na rūpāyatanaṁ na rūpanti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:47.1":{"pli":"Rūpāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na rūpāyatanaṁ, rūpaṁ. Rūpañca rūpāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva rūpaṁ na ca rūpāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:48.1":{"pli":"Na saddo na saddāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:49.1":{"pli":"Na saddāyatanaṁ na saddoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:50.1":{"pli":"Na gandho na gandhāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:51.1":{"pli":"Na gandhāyatanaṁ na gandhoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:52.1":{"pli":"Sīlagandho samādhigandho paññāgandho na gandhāyatanaṁ, gandho. Gandhañca gandhāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva gandho na ca gandhāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:53.1":{"pli":"Na raso na rasāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:54.1":{"pli":"Na rasāyatanaṁ na rasoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:55.1":{"pli":"Attharaso dhammaraso vimuttiraso na rasāyatanaṁ, raso. Rasañca rasāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva raso na ca rasāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:56.1":{"pli":"Na phoṭṭhabbo na phoṭṭhabbāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:57.1":{"pli":"Na phoṭṭhabbāyatanaṁ na phoṭṭhabboti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:58.1":{"pli":"Na mano na manāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:59.1":{"pli":"Na manāyatanaṁ na manoti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:60.1":{"pli":"Na dhammo na dhammāyatananti? Āmantā. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:61.1":{"pli":"Na dhammāyatanaṁ na dhammoti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:62.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso na dhammāyatanaṁ, dhammo. Dhammañca dhammāyatanañca ṭhapetvā avasesaṁ na ceva dhammo na ca dhammāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:63.0.1":{"pli":"3.1.2.2. Padasodhanamūlacakkavāra ","html":"<h2>{}</h2>"},"ya3.1.2:63.0.2":{"pli":"3.1.2.2.1. Anuloma ","html":"<h3>{}</h3>"},"ya3.1.2:63.1":{"pli":"Cakkhu cakkhāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:64.1":{"pli":"Dibbacakkhu paññācakkhu cakkhu, na cakkhāyatanaṁ. Cakkhāyatanaṁ cakkhu ceva cakkhāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:65.1":{"pli":"Āyatanā sotāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:66.1":{"pli":"Sotāyatanaṁ āyatanañceva sotāyatanañca. Avasesā āyatanā na sotāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:67.1":{"pli":"Cakkhu cakkhāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:68.1":{"pli":"Dibbacakkhu paññācakkhu cakkhu, na cakkhāyatanaṁ. Cakkhāyatanaṁ cakkhu ceva cakkhāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:69.1":{"pli":"Āyatanā ghānāyatananti …pe… āyatanā dhammāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:70.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ āyatanañceva dhammāyatanañca. Avasesā āyatanā na dhammāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:71.1":{"pli":"Sotaṁ sotāyatananti? …pe… Avasesā āyatanā na dhammāyatanaṁ …pe…. ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:72.1":{"pli":"Dhammo dhammāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:73.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso dhammo, na dhammāyatanaṁ. Dhammāyatanaṁ dhammo ceva dhammāyatanañca. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:74.1":{"pli":"Āyatanā cakkhāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='reverse'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:75.1":{"pli":"Cakkhāyatanaṁ āyatanañceva cakkhāyatanañca. Avasesā āyatanā na cakkhāyatanaṁ. ","html":"<p>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:76.1":{"pli":"Dhammo dhammāyatananti? ","html":"<p data-direction='forward'>{}</p>"},"ya3.1.2:77.1":{"pli":"Dhammāyatanaṁ ṭhapetvā avaseso dhammo, na dhammāyatanaṁ. Dhammāyatanaṁ dha